@REMARK =========================================================================
@NODE 9 "Title screen"

        Title screen, is just a screen........

        When you run the game. You'll watch the Backyard Brothers logo, then
you'll see a text screen, read it, and finally title screen.

        You can read the scroller (jumper?) text, now you can pres;

        F1: for info screen

        F2: for credits screen

        F3: for hi-scorelist

        Fire-Space-KeyPad '5': to skip to options.

        After some time, title screen will be replaced by info, credits and
hi-score screen... Press Fire-Space-KeyPad '5' to skip these.

@ENDNODE
