@NODE 15 "HISTORY"

pre     Uploaded to Aminet and released in some of Aminet CDs. as a @{"preview" link PRE}
        version.

1.89    Released after a looooooooooooong delay with lots of features and
        extras and levels.

1.90    This version.. Added the speed option... One more extra world
        released.





----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Wonder why we start from 1.89????

We gave the version number 1.00 to the preview, everytime we add a new thing
to the game we add 0.01 to the number... You might guess we did a lot since
preview.....

